OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FEngland are gearing up to play Ghana
OL,7,Fin their latest World Cup match on
OL,8,FTuesday evening.
OL,10,FA win would guarantee the Three Lions'
OL,11,Fprogression to the last 32 in the
OL,12,Ftournament, and a loss for Panama, who
OL,13,Fplay Croatia later that evening, would
OL,14,Fsecure England's position at the top
OL,15,Fof the group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
