OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782195489
OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FAfter playing their first match under
OL,7,Fa roof in the air-conditioned AT&T
OL,8,FStadium in Dallas, England's trip to
OL,9,FBoston Stadium looks set to be their
OL,10,Ffirst test in the hot and humid
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FHowever, the weather forecast for
OL,14,FTuesday is looking more favourable
OL,15,Fwith cloud, rain and much cooler
OL,16,Ftemperatures. It will still be in the
OL,17,Fmid-20s, but much more manageable than
OL,18,FEngland were expecting, which could
OL,19,Fallow the team to flourish.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
