OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FGhana are currently 65th in the world,
OL,7,Fmaking them England's weakest
OL,8,Fopponents of the group stage in terms
OL,9,Fof ranking.
OL,11,FThomas Tuchel's side will be very much
OL,12,Fthe favourites, but Ghana have a
OL,13,Fweapon that England know very well, as
OL,14,FManchester City star Antoine Semenyo
OL,15,Fwill provide a big threat.
OL,17,FSemenyo lit up the Premier League
OL,18,Ffollowing his mid-season move to the
OL,19,FEtihad Stadium, and England's defence
OL,20,Fwill have to be on guard to keep the
OL,21,F26-year-old London-born winger quiet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
