OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FAhead of the match, Marcus Rashford
OL,7,Fcalled for unrelenting intensity that
OL,8,FGhana "can't live with" as England
OL,9,Flook to book their place in the World
OL,10,FCup knockout stages with a game to
OL,11,Fspare.
OL,13,FThomas Tuchel's men opened Group L
OL,14,Fwith a 4-2 victory against Croatia in
OL,15,FDallas, where Harry Kane's brace in a
OL,16,Fhelter-skelter opening period was
OL,17,Ffollowed by a statement second-half
OL,18,Fdisplay.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
