OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,F"I think we have to bring an intensity
OL,7,Fthat they can't live with and we try
OL,8,Fand stick to that," the forward told
OL,9,Fthe Football Association.
OL,11,F"If we can play at that level, it can
OL,12,Fwin you games.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,F"The one thing we can predict is how
OL,20,Fwe conduct ourselves over 90 minutes
OL,21,For 120 minutes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]sD@AOU{D@AOU
