PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782195489
OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,F"So, I think we just have to focus on
OL,7,Fthat as players. We just have to keep
OL,8,Fpushing ourselves. We're definitely
OL,9,Fcapable."
OL,11,FOn Monday, Bukayo Saka rejoined the
OL,12,FEngland squad to train ahead of
OL,13,FTuesday's match against Ghana, after
OL,14,Fbeing absent from last Saturday's open
OL,15,Ftraining session following an Achilles
OL,16,Finjury.
OL,18,FEngland travelled to Massachusetts
OL,19,Fafter the session ahead of taking on
OL,20,FGhana at Gillette Stadium.
