OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FThe England team are seeking to
OL,7,Freplicate their second-half display
OL,8,Fagainst Croatia in Boston, where
OL,9,Fvictory against Ghana will seal their
OL,10,Fplace in the next round, with a match
OL,11,Fto go.
OL,13,FEngland would also head into
OL,14,FSaturday's final Group L game against
OL,15,FPanama as pool winners should the
OL,16,Fcentral American nation fail to beat
OL,17,FCroatia later on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
