OL,3,CEngland prepare to face Ghana as they
OL,4,Clook to top World Cup group
OL,6,FThat outcome would allow Tuchel to
OL,7,Frotate and rest star names at MetLife
OL,8,FStadium, where they hope to return on
OL,9,FJuly 19 for a shot at World Cup glory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
